    "description": "This carb smart recipe replaces half the white rice for cauliflower rice. This quick and easy rump steak stroganoff is the perfect option for a simple yet impressive meal. After searing the steak, you'll make a rich, creamy sauce in the pan to lock in all the flavours. Serve with rice and fresh parsley, you'll be rushing to the table for this one!",
